text: The Ambassador of Malaysia to the Holy See is the head of Malaysia's diplomatic mission to the Holy See. The position has the rank and status of an Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary and is based in the Embassy of Malaysia, Holy See. ==List of heads of mission== ===Ambassadors to the Holy See=== {| class=wikitable !
